Title: Mono ambiente amplio y confortable
Description:
Mono ambiente confortable en pleno centro de Corrientes a 20 metros de la peatonal Junin.

The space
Confortable y amplio mono ambiente en pleno centro de la ciudad. Cuenta con vigilancia de seguridad las 24 hs.


Hall de ingreso. Tres ascensores.


Ingreso y salida disponible a cualquier hora

Title: Departamento muy bien ubicado!
Description:
Welcome to our cozy 2BR apartment that comfortably accommodates 4 guests. You'll have access to a fully equipped kitchen, two bedrooms - one with a queen-sized bed and another with two single beds, a living room with cable TV, covered parking, and 24-hour security. Our location is perfect - just 3 blocks from the beach, 2 blocks from the Administrative Center, and 7 blocks from the city center.

We welcome well-behaved small/medium dogs, but kindly request that they don't sleep on the beds.


Two bedrooms - one with a queen-sized bed, two bedside tables, and a spacious wardrobe. The other bedroom has two single beds, a shared bedside table, and two wardrobes. Both bedrooms have fans and air conditioning (hot/cold).

The living room is spacious and has air conditioning (hot/cold), a dining table with four comfortable chairs, a sofa (not suitable for sleeping), and a smart TV with cable service.

The kitchen is fully equipped with a refrigerator, gas stove (with gas detector), coffee maker, electric kettle, and a table with two chairs. Utensils such as knives, forks, plates, glasses, a frying pan, a pot, etc., are included to accommodate up to 4 people.

The bathroom is complete with a bidet, an air extractor, and a high-quality shower with excellent water pressure and temperature.

The apartment is located in a modern building and has its own parking space.


Guests will have access to all areas of the apartment and the garage. The building does not have relevant common spaces.

A trescientos  metros del Parque Mitre  el pulmon verde de la ciudad de Corrientes,   y sobre el Rio Parana, se encuentra este departamento para dos personas. Lugar muy cerca del Campus Sargento Cabral de la Universidad Nacional del Nordeste  y de centros de recreaci√≥n como el Parque Mitre para realizar actividades deportivas o de esparcimiento y de la Costanera correntina. Corrientes es la cuna del Carnaval Argentino con un  historia que hace a la cultura de la Provincia, y a sus tradiciones. Esta fiesta se celebra entre los meses de enero y febrero.

Title: If you can't sit still, visit Corrientes!
Description:
This was our home for about 14 years. Only in 2020, with my husband, we decided to share it with others.

IMPORTANT: WiFi is not recommended for TELEWORK!

The space
Basic decoration, well lit.

The accommodation is about 2.5 km from the city center. Nearby (from 100 to 400 m) there are supermarkets, Rotisserie, Pharmacy, Laundries, Parking (not belonging to the accommodation) and several green spaces.

About 600 meters away is the M. T. Cocomarola amphitheater (Festival del Chamame and Recitals) and 400 meters from the Hurac√°n Corrientes Stadium (Most of the recitals are held there).

On the ground floor there is the kitchen/dining room, a sofa-bed, a mini gym, stationary bike, elliptical and an Ab Prince Pro.

On the upper floor (there is a staircase) is the bedroom and the bathroom, a space that can function as a desk and a balcony.


Guests enter and exit through a separate entrance and can make use of all of the above.


It has two floors connected by a staircase, for this reason it is not recommended for people with motor disabilities or small children or small pets.
